OL,6,FPolice believe there may be other
OL,7,Fvictims of a serial burglar who
OL,8,Fsexually assaulted one woman and stole
OL,9,Funderwear and sex toys during multiple
OL,10,Fbreak-ins.
OL,12,FFerence Bogdan, 33, was last week
OL,13,Fjailed for 16 years and 10 months for
OL,14,Fsix offences across Huddersfield.
OL,16,FDet Ch Insp Ian Thornes, of Kirklees
OL,17,FDistrict Police, said Bogdan, of
OL,18,FPollard Street in Fartown, was "a real
OL,19,Fdanger to women".
