OL,6,FLeeds Crown Court heard Bogdan twice
OL,7,Fbroke into a property on Ashbrow Road
OL,8,Fin Huddersfield in November 2023,
OL,9,Fstealing personal items on the first
OL,10,Foccasion and intending to commit a
OL,11,Fsexual offence on the second.
OL,13,FIn September 2024 he broke into an
OL,14,Faddress on Ridding Road and stole sex
OL,15,Ftoys.
OL,17,FLater that month he sexually assaulted
OL,18,Fa woman inside a house he broke into
OL,19,Fbut fled after the victim fought back.
OL,20,FHe was arrested a short time later.
